<p>This was definitely one of the issues that was happening. We discovered that we were supplying it only 5v which is not good. Unfortunately we have not tested to see if this was the only issue but it seemed to make things better. There was also some <span class="abbreviation">CAN<template class="tooltiptext" data-text="Controller Area Network"></template></span> issues that were causing the CANdle to have connectivity issues.</p>
